Titolo: Drug Wars (video game)

Anno: 1984

Descrizione: Drugwars is a turn-based strategy computer game in which the player assumes the role of a drug dealer engaged in arbitrage. The object of the game is to deal the most drugs to pay off the "loan shark" (who charges interest) by the end of the game and make a profit. Inspired by the text-based BASIC game Star Trader, Drugwars was originally an MS-DOS program created by John E. Dell in 1984.

Genere: Turn-based

Valutazione: N/A
